651
00:34:14,080 --> 00:34:15,760
Stop.

652
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,000
Go back with me.

653
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:18,880
Mom.

654
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:22,679
Tao.

655
00:34:26,080 --> 00:34:27,280
Are you okay?

656
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:28,880
I heard

657
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:30,280
