692
00:37:33,460 --> 00:37:34,800
What can we do?

693
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:40,240
Chen, I have a way.

694
00:37:41,179 --> 00:37:45,999
<i>[Tianlin Animal Hospital]</i>

695
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:16,720
